<div class="hgroup"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">Napsauta, raahaa tai vieritä kosketuslevyllä</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents"><p class="p">If your system has a touchpad, you can click, double-click, drag, and scroll using only your
touchpad, without separate hardware buttons.</p></div>
<div id="clickordrag" class="sect"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">Click or drag</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="p">You can click or drag using your touchpad.</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Click the <span class="em">system menu</span> <span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/system-devices-panel.svg" class="media media-inline" alt="Power cog icon"></span></span> and
    select <span class="gui">System Settings</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Avaa <span class="gui">Hiiri ja kosketuslevy</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Valitse <span class="gui">Kosketuslevy</span>-kohdasta valinta <span class="gui">Napsauta napauttamalla</span>.</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
<div class="list"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ul class="list" style="list-style-type:disc">
<li class="list"><p class="p">To click, tap once (but not in the bottom or top right-hand corners).</p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">Kaksoisnapsautus onnistuu napauttamalla kosketuslevyä kahdesti.</p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">To drag an item, tap twice but don't lift your finger after the second tap.
Drag the item where you want it, then lift your finger to drop.</p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">To right-click, tap once in the bottom right-hand corner.</p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">To middle-click, tap once in the top right-hand corner.</p></li>
</ul></div></div></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
<div id="twofingerscroll" class="sect"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">Kahden sormen vieritys</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="p">Voit vierittää kahdella sormella käyttäen kosketuslevyä.</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Click the <span class="em">system menu</span> <span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/system-devices-panel.svg" class="media media-inline" alt="Power cog icon"></span></span> and
    select <span class="gui">System Settings</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Avaa <span class="gui">Hiiri ja kosketuslevy</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Valitse <span class="gui">Kosketuslevy</span>-kohdasta valinta <span class="gui">Kahden sormen vieritys</span>.</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
<p class="p">When this is selected, tapping and dragging with one finger will work as
normal, but if you drag two fingers across any part of the touchpad, it will
scroll instead. If you also select <span class="gui">Enable horizontal scrolling</span>, you
can move your fingers left and right to scroll horizontally. Be careful to space
your fingers a bit apart. If your fingers are too close together, they just look
like one big finger to your touchpad.</p>
<div class="note" title="Huomautus"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">Kahden sormen vieritys ei välttämättä toimi kaikilla kosketuslevyillä.</p></div></div></div></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
<div id="contentsticks" class="sect"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">Luonnollinen vieritys</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="p">You can drag content as if sliding a physical piece of paper using the
touchpad.</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Click the <span class="em">system menu</span> <span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/system-devices-panel.svg" class="media media-inline" alt="Power cog icon"></span></span> and
    select <span class="gui">System Settings</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Avaa <span class="gui">Hiiri ja kosketuslevy</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">In the <span class="gui">Touchpad</span> section, check
   <span class="gui">Content sticks to fingers</span>.</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
<div class="note" title="Huomautus"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">This feature is also known as <span class="em">Natural Scrolling</span> or
<span class="em">Reverse Scrolling</span>.</p></div></div></div></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
